name: Children love rituals
description:
In month of Muharram people of our village do many rituals.From free food to playing Ta'zieh, Children are biggest fans of rituals. They love holding a flag which they can not read. They love being a part of it happily, although the whole month is for mourning and grief, it's interestingly paradoxical how happy kids are during it.
